      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from coupon testing of same alloy heat as production screws; geometry from nominal CAD with dimensional inspection confirmation.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.1 GPa) were drawn from the 2018 Ti-6Al-4V coupon dataset. Geometry was extracted from nominal CAD and confirmed by CMM inspection of three production screws. Input uncertainty propagation was not performed at this gradation level. Gradation 2 achieved."
