      "acceptanceCriteria": "N=11 constructs from production lots, dimensional inspection confirms conformance to nominal geometry within drawing tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs from two production lots were tested. Dimensional inspection of all screws and rods confirmed conformance to nominal drawing dimensions within ±0.05 mm. Sample size provides adequate statistical basis for mean comparison at Gradation 2."
