      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate COU loading environment including load rate, fixture geometry, and environmental conditions across at least two independent configurations.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single load rate (5 mm/min) and single fixture geometry per ASTM F1717. No variation in load rate or fixture offset was explored. Environmental conditions (ambient temperature, dry) are consistent between labs but do not span the physiological range. Gradation 1 achieved; below required Gradation 2. This factor is flagged as a known gap."
    },
