      "rationale": "CAD geometry used in FEA matches CMM-measured test articles within 0.03 mm RMS. Fixture grip geometry and load application point in the FEA replicate the physical test fixture as confirmed by fixture drawings. Boundary condition equivalency is documented in the V&V plan. Gradation 2 achieved."
