      "rationale": "Stiffness: 4.2% difference, E/uval = 0.87. Yield force: 6.8% difference, E/uval = 1.31. Force at 40 mm: 7.5% difference, E/uval = 1.44. All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. Gradation 2 achieved."
